{"analytics_identifier":"OT515","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-of-the-parliamentary-counsel","content_id":"9f80fe62-b229-4517-9e32-f560b5c518ce","description":"The Office of the Parliamentary Counsel is a group of government lawyers who specialise in drafting legislation. We work closely with departments to translate policy into clear, effective and readable law. Our role will often begin when legislation is first being considered and we will remain involved throughout the Parliamentary process and beyond. OPC is part of the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"OPC","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Office of the Parliamentary Counsel is a group of government lawyers who specialise in drafting legislation. We work closely with departments to translate policy into clear, effective and readable law. Our role will often begin when legislation is first being considered and we will remain involved throughout the Parliamentary process and beyond.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office of the Parliamentary Counsel\">OPC</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office of the Parliamentary Counsel"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/office-of-the-parliamentary-counsel/about/recruitment","title":"Working for OPC"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/new-first-parliamentary-counsel-appointed","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/663355df1834d96a0aa6cfaa/s712_s960_cabinet_office.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/663355df8603389a07a6cfaa/s465_s960_cabinet_office.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/663355df8603389a07a6cfa9/s960_cabinet_